Package org.sparadrap.model.PatientModel

Class Patient

java.lang.Object
org.sparadrap.model.AbstractEntity
org.sparadrap.model.PatientModel.Patient
public class Patient extends AbstractEntity
Represents a Patient in the system. Contains details such as social security number, last name, date of birth, treating doctor, insurance, and coverage percentage.
